Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:43.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:47.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,Please let me play, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.04,Background,,0,0,0,,If I let you play, you're going to win for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:58.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou, you've finally come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A handicap...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He'll have to play differently if he has a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:09.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll play with one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:15.11,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(325,115)}The Forty-Ninth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:15.11,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}A Painful Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Twenty minutes for him to play the first move...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:35.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What an unexpected beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:40.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Let's see how the Meijin responds to this move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.79,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hoshi on the lower right corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so stuffy in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time that\Nsomething like this has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look nervous though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun was here, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask him his thoughts about the\Nlong time he spent on the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Master Kuwabara!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That took some time. The match\Ndid start on time... Right, Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Shindou-kun surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He spent twenty minutes on the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note, Master Kuwabara,\Nare you here for Shindou-kun today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think highly of that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling when I passed by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Passed by? Are you basing\Nyour opinion of him only on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's his intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never beat me, Ogata-kun,\Nif you think so little of my intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:32.60,Background,,0,0,0,,Even if it is just intuition, it's impressive\Nthat he has Master Kuwabara's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.33,Background,,0,0,0,,Not just Master Kuwabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:42.78,Background,,0,0,0,,He has Mr. Ogata's too, and, Touya\NMeijin requested to play him for this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! He requested the game!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Requested?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Meijin is probably interested\Nbecause Akira-kun thinks of him as a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he your rival, Touya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.00,Background,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Meijin has to be interested\Nin the boy regardless of his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That man has good intuition, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:31.19,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)}Boushi is when you limit a stone's ability to expand into the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,13-14. Boushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Uh... Boushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Started a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This early in the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What is Shindou thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,13-17. Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,I won't stand a chance unless I fight early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him into a difficult battle.\NWhoever can read further will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:32.22,Sai,,0,0,0,,I have to create a weak\Npoint that he'll want to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,When my opponent comes to end the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.78,Sai,,0,0,0,,That is when black's path to victory will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,18-16. Suberi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,But... he isn't playing what I want him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.46,Sai,,0,0,0,,He's being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:43.52,Sai,,0,0,0,,If the game goes any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.57,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's only going to get more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.16,Sai,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,18-9. Osae!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Shindou-kun doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.32,Background,,0,0,0,,He's being way too aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.54,Background,,0,0,0,,All of his moves look hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He went too far here, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Black has a bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun, Shindou-kun\Nis far from being your rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Black's done for if he\Nloses these stones here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the kind of shape one would want to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But... my father didn't attack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's because he didn't\Nwant the game to end too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ogata-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that black is at a disadvantage. I\Nwonder what Master Touya thinks about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He has good intuition, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Black looks like it's about to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:35.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But it looks dangerous when I read far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It would probably be best if I\Ndon't get lured in right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:56.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This match... it looks poorly played.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But it is rather deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's a new first dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A fourteen year old child, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What is this atmosphere around him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What is this pressure I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:59.09,Background,,0,0,0,,The battle that started in the\Ncorner has spread across the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou probably wanted to\Nspread the battle across the board
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hopes of a mistake by his opponent. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The result is crystal clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Black's been wiped out! Wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master Touya sure is being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a good thing for young\Npeople to take risks, but he went too far here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way it would work against the Meijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.28,Background,,0,0,0,,It ended just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.30,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shindou-kun is disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're going to\Nstart the discussion over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I win the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it doesn't affect my opinion of Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an interesting match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-kun, I'm going to bet on the\Nboy again, if this ever happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.52,Background,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The match just now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:13:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense if the boy put a\Nlarge handicap on himself for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!? Put a handicap on himself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Against my father, the Meijin!? It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why he did that,\Nbut isn't he an interesting boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have liked to have\Nplayed without any handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you played the way you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still couldn't hide that something you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:07.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He didn't just find out that I\Nplaced a handicap on myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin's also gotten an idea of Sai's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a pressure from you similar to\Nthat of an extremely experienced player.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we play, let it be an even match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes, let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start from the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.28,Background,,0,0,0,,To put a handicap on himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What an interesting boy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I played him two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... as if I was playing my\Nfather. He seemed that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But... when I played him again six months later,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.98,Background,,0,0,0,,he was so weak he seemed like someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.59,Memory,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.73,Memory,,0,0,0,,T-Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,'I didn't chase after someone that weak as a rival.'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself... I got very angry over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But... one day he said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:51.94,Memory,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pass you by someday,\Nif you keep chasing after my illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time I saw him, he was an Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... he's facing my father\Nin the Room of Deep Contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one that pulled\Nhim into the world of the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya... what was your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira, I see. I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't say anything, no\Nmatter what anyone else asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, the record keeper said something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya supposedly said that he wanted\Nto play Shindou-kun in an even match next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Though, Touya\NMeijin didn't say so straight out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so Amano-san can't put it into the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:19.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,My father, the Meijin, said he\Nwanted to play Shindou in an even game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not getting on!? Touya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he saw through all your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Touya's dad sure is incredible. He\Nrealized that it wasn't just a poorly played game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.38,Memory,,0,0,0,,Next time, let it be an even match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.97,Memory,,0,0,0,,Yes, let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:55.24,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you want to play an even game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:56.68,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,I wonder!? But, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it happen someday. Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.11,Sai,,0,0,0,,When is this 'someday'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,'Someday' is 'someday'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it was an important match for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't play it because of\Nyour selfishness, don't you get that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:30.89,Sai,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it was your fault for coming to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Shuusaku better, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike me, Shuusaku let\Nyou play all the games, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, you called him Torajirou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.73,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs15.5\bord0.5\shad0\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz13\pos(246,205)}The\NHint\Nto Tsumego
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:50.86,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs15.5\bord0.5\shad0\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz21\pos(235,197)}The\NHint\Nto Tsumego
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:50.98,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs15.5\bord0.5\shad0\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz33\pos(222,183)}The\NHint\Nto Tsumego
