Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:51.49,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs15.5\bord0.5\shad0\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz53\pos(260,31)}The\NHint\Nto Tsumego
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:51.65,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs15.5\bord0.5\shad0\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz53\pos(311,-62)}The\NHint\Nto Tsumego
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:55.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder why Torajirou didn't want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he want to become a Go player?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a boring guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:05.84,Sai,,0,0,0,,That's... that's my... my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,I was impatient when I returned to the real world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,and I didn't know that I\Nwould get to meet you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:17.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,So I demanded a lot of Torajirou,\Nbecause I didn't want to lose this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what... did Torajirou die\Nan early death because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:31.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,N-No! Torajirou was a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:35.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,When there was an epidemic, and\Npeople around him began to get sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,he watched over them at\Nthe risk of getting sick himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:39.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,He was a very clever...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,and truly kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying is\Nthat I'm stupid and unkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After your game today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,did you say to Shindou Hikaru that you\Nwished to play him in an even match next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:31.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru made my father, the Meijin, say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Just who is Shindou?
