Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:00.49,Sai,,0,0,0,,I am Sai of the Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:07.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,The reason I have been in the world for a\Nthousand years, is just to master the divine move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:10.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:12.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,But why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:25.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,God! Why did I come to Hikaru!?
